reviewText: Great DVD worth buying for Cory Lane and Chrissy Moran

All of the sneaky previews I have seen have been good.  This one is a good one as well.  I got it for Crissy Moran and the cover girl Cory Lane.  I have seen Crissy before and like her a lot as she is very friendly but then all the womrn on these discs are friendly.
